Class PitchModulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.effect.sound.PitchModulation

  • public final class PitchModulation
extends Object
    Represents a value to supply to Viewer.playSound(SoundType, Vector3d, double) to modulate the pitch to a specified note.
